&lt;p&gt;You’ll work closely with a cross-disciplinary team across both challenger and enterprise accounts. You’ll be charged with managing performance, driving growth and&amp;nbsp; to shift thinking beyond basic campaign tactics and connect the dots with broader business objectives and outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
