&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will have experience in Amazon DSP and paid search campaign strategy, management, and execution as this role will focus on supporting Commerce accounts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, launch, and optimize paid search and DSP campaigns across Retail Media accounts (Amazon, Walmart, Target) with a focus on strategy building and flawless execution and exceeding KPIs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help optimize campaigns in a never ending quest to improve results for our clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generate reports for both internal teams and the client to indicate performance and trends across keywords, ad groups, campaigns, ad copy and more.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recommend and implement optimizations to existing campaigns to improve overall performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform campaign QA on your own campaigns, plus those built by others on the team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide data and insights to in-market teams for campaign wrap-ups and larger reporting deliverables such as QBRs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all client campaigns are properly pacing to the aligned upon budget&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who will love this role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A self-starter who is comfortable working in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A critical thinker who enjoys analyzing large datasets to uncover compelling insights from campaign data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A curious, strategic mind that embraces lifelong learning and collaboration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A meticulous organizer with a proven ability to manage multiple projects at a time while meeting tight deadlines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A dedicated learner who is comfortable receiving and incorporating feedback to support their continued growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You should have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of hands-on campaign activation experience across Amazon DSP and Amazon search campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience activating campaigns across awareness, consideration and conversion objectives&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with data hygiene, analysis, and visualization in Google Sheets and/or Microsoft Excel. Pivot table experience is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to manage multiple projects at a time while paying strict attention to detail and meeting deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
